Company Overview of Waste Management & Recycling Products Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
As of April 27, 2010, Waste Management & Recycling Products Inc. was acquired by Colt Refining, Inc. Waste Management & Recycling Products Inc. provides electronics recycling solutions. Its services include electronics recycling, removal/pickup, asset recovery, equipment buyouts and purchases, physical and data destruction, warehousing/storage, evaluations and consultations, appraisal, refurbishing and reuse, and inventory services and detailed reporting, as well as disassembly, demanufacturing, and destruction services; and transportation, logistics, packaging, and on-site labor solutions. The company accepts various types of electronics for recycling, such as computers, computer boards, CR...
As of April 27, 2010, Waste Management & Recycling Products Inc. was acquired by Colt Refining, Inc. Waste Management & Recycling Products Inc. provides electronics recycling solutions. Its services include electronics recycling, removal/pickup, asset recovery, equipment buyouts and purchases, physical and data destruction, warehousing/storage, evaluations and consultations, appraisal, refurbishing and reuse, and inventory services and detailed reporting, as well as disassembly, demanufacturing, and destruction services; and transportation, logistics, packaging, and on-site labor solutions. The company accepts various types of electronics for recycling, such as computers, computer boards, CRTs, hard drives, modems, computer accessories and components, cables and printers, office electronics and equipment, medical equipment, and telephones systems and communications equipment. It also resells used and surplus computer systems and electronics, including laptops, hard drives, wireless laptop cards, LCD monitors, and surge protectors for power and telephone; and Spy Sweeper, a tool for detecting, removing, and blocking spyware. The company was incorporated in 1989 and is based in Schenectady, New York.
Detailed Description


